This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image reconstruction. The use of a stacked denoising autoencoder (SDAE) also suggests that it may belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions compressed sensing and Kalman filtering, which are techniques commonly used in signal processing (cs.NE and cs.IT). Finally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which could also place it in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
